was in the way so we could not move into ToV, me still <br>
having dubious CoV faction went up to Sontalak and <br>
harmonied him so everyone could move by him.<br>
(much easier than training him away)<br>
<br>
But after the raid now i am also KOS to Sontalak, my question<br>
is could i still move into the range of the harmony spell <br>
without getting in the agro range of Sontalak?<br>
(heard he doesn't have a really large agro range)<br>
<br>
Anyone have some first hand experience on this?<br>
<br>
